Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命巨杉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(462,670)}Druid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森咒使所使用的召喚術之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其散發著綠色光輝的樹蔭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能間歇性地恢復隊友們的Hp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的判斷 依靠那個咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有十個人的Hp可以恢復30%以上
