Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因果驅動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.00,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}*因果驅動：恢復輔助型魔法：效果持續中，攻擊產生暴擊效果時大幅度恢復該單位Mp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊布拉哈布拉的AOE攻擊 「無慈悲的煉獄之宴」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約有180秒CD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(596,670)}Mercy Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(882,670)}Life Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次的攻擊由沃寧的恩惠之雨 以及加速治癒技能抵禦過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再下一次就是360秒後了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(793,670)}Castle Of Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那一次 則用直擊CD好了的磐石堡壘使其無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,540秒後的再下一次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Aurora Heal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,則用特托拉的極光女神之治癒來恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(720,670)}Karma Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛才設置的因果驅動的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對伊布拉哈布拉的攻擊產生暴擊效果的話 就會大量恢復Mp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.00,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\an7}吐槽：鋼琴手的福音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續以現在的輸出速度計算的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再有約700秒就可以給BOSS最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再之後 將全部的戰力都轉移到塔爾塔烏魯加那邊進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的 維持現在的DPS就能獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽到了嗎 腹黑這樣說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神擊敗BOSS 不要吝嗇你們的輸出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒法打啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產生數量與給予黑騎士模式下的路賽亞特傷害的人數相同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然之前預測會有幾隻沒有清理乾淨的會追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這次在移動到大空洞之前 影子小怪應該已經全部被打掉了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使路賽亞特恢復成黑模式 也沒有人能在那個區域給他造成傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己對自己造成傷害？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過一段時間 又會恢復到黑騎士模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每當恢復到黑模式 就與產生的影子小兵一起對自己造成傷害…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟產生了多少小怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約200秒產生一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果按指數級增加的話…現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,31只？62只？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是31只的話還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有600秒就能將伊布拉哈布拉打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近戰 放風箏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得有人去拉住影子小兵的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉出這片戰場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊然後放風箏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}WyvernKick
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘲諷呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}TauntingShout
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米迪米真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全給我跟過來 影子小兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴 混蛋眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}WyvernKick
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會都到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道他想要把Raid搞砸來向我復仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 但是這個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神閃電
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}MindBolt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為裝備在迪米卡斯身上的固定炮台來持續掩護的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去塔爾塔烏魯加那邊的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 憑什麼指揮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個前搖是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「塔爾塔烏魯加的白夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附加移動阻礙效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山貓的躲閃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}LinksTumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠！喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉 打倒敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！迪米迪米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 腹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}MindShock
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元靈束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Astralbind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風箏放的還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時候開始就一直無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也許是因為混亂 做出了極端的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使這樣 還是無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 離太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經看不到影子小怪們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們回到大空洞去 就得不償失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋賦予
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米卡斯我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「記錄的地平線」的城惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(582,670)}Log Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你鬧哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠 你到那前面死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子的葬身之地也不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這前面？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的棧道的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(563,670)}Abyssal Shaft
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目標…終點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我一點都不想歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,555)}但又不得不這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到達的奈落的棧道的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(659,670)}Abyssal Shaft
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在那裡的黃金的大鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.69,0:24:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等候城惠多時的是最後的RaidBoss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.67,0:24:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第九庭院的烏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和供贄一族的菫星
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在終於被揭開的城惠想法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真正的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 供贄的黃金
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屹立起來吧 再一次
